oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Cash, June Carter (portrait)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Valerie June Carter was born June 29th, 1929, in Maces Spring, Virginia, into the famous Carter Family, known for its country music singing. June was playing with the group by 1939. Carter, the wife of the late Johnny Cash, died in Nashville in 2003.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Singers; Women
